name: camouflage karmamäleon
description: digitaldrawing 6000x6000px, revisited a drawing i made a few years ago when i started to crawl out of a deep dark mental hole.it was about hiding my inner world and how to cope with expectations. it wasnˋt planned and just evolved, i quite still like it and enjoyed to play with this sketch, this is how this series "camouflage" of five singleeditions came out.
